Episode.Overview: Carla and Elliot try to help a patient, Maggie, lose her virginity as she prepares to die. Walking in on her sister and Dr. Cox prompts Danni to move in with J.D. But a personal grudge seems to stand in the way and may decide whether the patient lives or dies.
